<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HostelNode - Smart Hostel Management</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
        }
        .buttons {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff7e5f;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            margin: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 126, 95, 0.4);
        }
        .feature-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 15px;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            transition: 0.3s;
            animation: slideUp 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to HostelNode</h1>
        <p>Smart Hostel Management Software to automate room allocation, fee tracking, and reporting.</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
            <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-cards">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Room & Bed Management</h3>
                <p>Easily assign and manage hostel rooms and beds.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Automated Fee Tracking</h3>
                <p>Generate invoices and send reminders automatically.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Real-time Reporting</h3>
                <p>Monitor occupancy, revenue, and pending dues.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Multi-Hostel Support</h3>
                <p>Manage multiple hostels from a single dashboard.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>User Roles & Security</h3>
                <p>Role-based access control for admins and staff.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Automated Notifications</h3>
                <p>Send fee reminders and important updates via email/SMS.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>